# IELTS Task 1 高级表达与句式整理（7.5-8.0核心）

你现在其实最需要的不是“模板”。

而是：

# 真正的 Task 1 学术表达系统（Academic Reporting Language）

因为：

Task 1 本质不是英语作文。

而是：

# 数据报告（data report）

高分的关键：

不是词汇量大。

而是：

* 会 overview
* 会比较
* 会概括
* 会避免重复
* 会用 academic report language

下面我给你整理：

1. 开头句高级表达
2. Overview 万能句型
3. 数据表达
4. 比较表达
5. 趋势图表达
6. 流程图表达
7. 地图题表达
8. 高分连接词
9. Band 8 高频词块
10. 真正的8分写法思维

这套建议你长期积累。

---

# 一、开头句高级表达（Introduction）

---

# 1. 图表题万能表达

## 普通：

> The chart shows...

## 8分：

> The chart illustrates...

> The graph depicts...

> The table compares...

> The diagram demonstrates...

---

# 2. 多图组合表达

## 高分模板：

> The pie chart illustrates ..., while the table compares ...

例如：

> The pie chart illustrates the destinations of graduates, while the table compares their salaries after five years of employment.

---

# 3. “关于……”高级表达

| 普通                      | 高级                         |
| ----------------------- | -------------------------- |
| about                   | regarding                  |
| shows                   | provides information about |
| gives information about | presents data on           |

---

# 二、Overview（最重要）

# Overview 决定 Task Achievement

没有 overview：

# 基本不可能 7+

---

# 1. Overview 核心句型

## 万能句：

> Overall, it is clear that...

---

# 2. 极高频高级表达

| 普通        | 高级                     |
| --------- | ---------------------- |
| biggest   | dominant               |
| smallest  | minimal                |
| increased | showed an upward trend |
| decreased | experienced a decline  |

---

# 3. Overview 模板（超级重要）

## 动态图：

> Overall, it is evident that X increased significantly, whereas Y experienced a downward trend.

---

## 静态图：

> Overall, X accounted for the largest proportion, while Y represented the smallest category.

---

## 流程图：

> Overall, the process is linear and consists of X stages, beginning with ... and ending with ...

---

# 三、数据表达（Task1 核心）

---

# 1. 百分比高级表达

| 数据  | 高分表达             |
| --- | ---------------- |
| 50% | half             |
| 52% | just over half   |
| 48% | just under half  |
| 25% | a quarter        |
| 75% | three quarters   |
| 5%  | a small minority |
| 80% | a vast majority  |

---

# 2. 占比表达

## 普通：

> X was 20%.

## 高分：

> X accounted for 20%.

> X represented 20%.

> 20% of ...

---

# 3. 高级比例表达

> The figure stood at 20%.

> The proportion reached 30%.

> The percentage amounted to 15%.

---

# 四、比较表达（Band 8 必备）

---

# 1. 基础比较

| 普通          | 高级              |
| ----------- | --------------- |
| more than   | exceeded        |
| less than   | remained below  |
| bigger than | was higher than |

---

# 2. 高级比较句型

> X was considerably higher than Y.

> X exceeded Y by approximately 20%.

> In contrast to X, Y remained relatively low.

---

# 3. 对比连接（极重要）

